{"tid":226430,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"［返工辛苦篇］我好苦惱","createTime":"2017-05-02T13:42:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-05T04:48:58.000Z","uid":84382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"903fb6dcc47ce631ef4448d3e707f83b6cd01327","tid":226430,"uid":84382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T13:42:06.000Z","msg":"最近晚晚都OT好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今晚又辛苦開夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好想有個人可以攬下錫下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係好寂寞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做咗23年人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中學又話唔俾拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大學又話GPA緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點知畢業又要衝事業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n啱啱睇住張CAD 檔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我喊咗出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n阿Sir 見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢叫我洗個面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 落街食個晚餐再上黎拼搏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我屌佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢竟然係叫我食完晚餐再上黎做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而唔係叫我早d收工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但身為一個打工族<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我有得揀咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我死死氣咁離開office <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我行又行<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我唔知我要去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔經唔覺我行咗入間譚仔<br />\n<br />\n我竟然見到d咁既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/02/214137_ebc9772cafdb65491fdf3fee69f488e3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F02%2F214137_ebc9772cafdb65491fdf3fee69f488e3.jpg&h=9a0faea7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我覺得我係零<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我什麼也不是<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8dc400fe4ab15916dc0ce9ae77906ecbfef10fc","tid":226430,"uid":84382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T13:43:38.000Z","msg":"如果可以㨂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我唔想生存係香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7659b5a9dc8d3a681340d785b3f9d3af1d06baba","tid":226430,"uid":84382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T13:44:24.000Z","msg":"壓力好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae457c0611a901df382b4078c140f7c1ba462e81","tid":226430,"uid":73613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T13:44:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e7f7b254492e76758c7c1a1147de291a7904e827","tid":226430,"uid":84382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T13:46:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>工程顧問?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 接近 但唔係顧問"},{"pid":"cf949ff27f25cabbf2d63276d2405b557382b7df","tid":226430,"uid":84382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T13:47:42.000Z","msg":"女呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我好想要女呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5129cfb88ce3d5bd83528083c288a63a6a8f9f2","tid":226430,"uid":84382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T13:49:47.000Z","msg":"其實叫雞係咪解脫？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得我得返呢條路可以㨂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eea748e477962c460d1f219707b69985589380e","tid":226430,"uid":84382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T13:50:52.000Z","msg":"今晚都唔知可以幾點走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f795b24c4a94d7923c122e4b513165ae7f9cc25","tid":226430,"uid":37620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T13:53:03.000Z","msg":"CAD file..即係咩工？"},{"pid":"041a4ed823437314387c6ec26e8a129eadcfb5bb","tid":226430,"uid":84382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T13:53:04.000Z","msg":"我就黎痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3b4e258939e7553b8710654b8c29dad72c0118a","tid":226430,"uid":44626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T17:48:09.000Z","msg":"同樓主同樣case <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6025988b0b536a35670d06a69ae52dffce480316","tid":226430,"uid":33866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T04:48:58.000Z","msg":"工程狗就係抵撚死"}]}